$c = random(2,5,1);
$d = random(2,5,1);
$e = random(2,5,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
The expression \(\sqrt{x^$a y^$b} \root 3 \of {x^$c y^$d}\root 5
 \of {x^$e}\) equals
\(x^ry^s\) $BR where r, the exponent of x, is:
\{ans_rule(20) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $a/2+$c/3+$e/5;
